{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","id":"msg_013wnHPrbkiAEBYiw9RqdRbi","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_01JcxuGaWrGdc79AKPftVZe8","name":"Edit","input":{"replace_all":false,"file_path":"/Users/michielgerritsen/Sites/mage-os-install/.chief/prds/main/progress.md","old_string":"## Codebase Patterns\n- Uses Bubble Tea TUI framework (`github.com/charmbracelet/bubbletea`) with a central `Model` and phase-based state machine\n- Text inputs use `github.com/charmbracelet/bubbles/textinput`\n- Phases are defined as `phase int` constants (e.g., `phaseNameInput`, `phaseDirectoryInput`, etc.)\n- Detection runs in background goroutine, results cached in model until user advances\n- Tests are in `internal/tui/tui_test.go` using `sendMsg()` helper to drive state transitions\n- Run tests with `/usr/local/go/bin/go test ./...`","new_string":"## Codebase Patterns\n- Uses Bubble Tea TUI framework (`github.com/charmbracelet/bubbletea`) with a central `Model` and phase-based state machine\n- Text inputs use `github.com/charmbracelet/bubbles/textinput`\n- Phases are defined as `phase int` constants (e.g., `phaseNameInput`, `phaseDirectoryInput`, etc.)\n- Detection runs in background goroutine, results cached in model until user advances\n- Tests are in `internal/tui/tui_test.go` using `sendMsg()` helper to drive state transitions\n- Run tests with `/usr/local/go/bin/go test ./...`\n- Detector tests live in `internal/detector/detector_test.go` and use `allDetectors()` (package-internal) to inspect all registered detectors\n- TUI view tests call `m.View()` directly and use a local `contains()` helper to assert rendered output"},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":120,"cache_read_input_tokens":58444,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":120},"output_tokens":55,"service_tier":"sta