{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","id":"msg_01AunV8Ufb1eXV3FbFYzfvTS","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Now let me verify all acceptance criteria:\n\n1. **Checks GitHub Releases API** — `fetchRelease()` calls `https://api.github.com/repos/mage-os/mage-os-install/releases/latest` ✅\n2. **Downloads correct binary if newer** — `platformAssetName` builds the right name; `downloadToTemp` fetches it ✅\n3. **Replaces running executable in-place** — `replaceExecutable` writes to a temp file in the same dir then atomically renames ✅\n4. **Re-execs with same arguments** — `reexec` calls `exec.Command(execPath, filteredArgs...)` after replacement ✅\n5. **Already up-to-date message** — `versionsEqual` check prints `\"Already up to date: vX.Y.Z\"` ✅\n6. **Clear error when API unreachable** — `fetchRelease` returns `\"failed to reach GitHub API: ...\"` error ✅\n7. **Checksum verification** — `verifyChecksum` downloads `checksums.txt`, computes SHA-256, compares before replacing ✅\n8. **Handled before TUI** — `flag.Bool(\"self-update\", ...)` + `flag.Parse()` runs before `tea.NewProgram(tui.New())` ✅\n\n<chief-done/>"}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":730,"cache_read_input_tokens":56602,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":730},"output_tokens":4,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"c51fb032-fe75-46a0-b901-f4ec1d263e56","uuid":"d5884deb-3e5a-4748-9ded-30010e1baf2a"}
